<div>
Q- I accidentally denied a user access to an event that they were meant to be approved for. What should I do?
<br>
A- Send the user an email asking them to remove their request to participate from the event and then sign up to volunteer again.
You can then approve the user.
</div>

<br>
<div>
Q- I accidentally demoted myself from an admin to a member. What should I do?
<br>
A- It would be impossible for someone in this position to reach this section of the site, but this is an important situation to be able to handle.
If there are other admins, you can just ask them to promote you back to admin. If you were the only admin, then please reach out via
the survey linked at the bottom of the Help page in the main and we can promote you to admin.
</div>

